  <official_title>A Phase 2 Open-Label Study to Assess the Pharmacodynamics, Pharmacokinetics, Safety and Tolerability of AKCEA-ANGPTL3-LRX (ISIS 703802) Administered Subcutaneously to Patients With Familial Chylomicronemia Syndrome (FCS)</official_title>
