  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a single center, open-label study to evaluate the efficacy of AKCEA-ANGPTL3-LRX for
      reduction of triglyceride (TG) levels in patients with Familial Chylomicronemia Syndrome
      (FCS) .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
